title: A home with a personal touch - Res Lease in Austin. 1 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Don’t miss out on this opportunity to lease this fabulous home with one bedroom and bathroom in Travis county, Austin, TX!', 'Just minutes from downtown and near outstanding schools and parks, such a convenient location!', 'You will love everything this lovely home offers: elegant wooden floors, an open concept floor plan, and plenty of windows that make this home so warm and inviting.', 'You will indeed create lovely memories in the well-designed kitchen equipped with must-have stainless steel appliances, beautiful wood cabinetry, and a pantry with plenty of space to utilize.', 'The main bedroom includes plush carpet, ample space, and an ensuite bathroom with single vanity and a nice tiled shower perfect for a relaxing bath after a long day at work.', 'Pets are welcome in this home, especially in the community green areas, so apply today to secure this home for you and your furry friends!!', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 6425463)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
